<br>
“What’s wrong?”<br>
<br>
“I ---” she paused as it took her a moment to remember where and, more importantly, *when* she was.  Chloe caught his hand as it stilled on her arm and gave it a reassuring squeeze.  “Nothing,” she lied.  “Just a bad dream.”<br>
<br>
“Hmm,” Bruce said and gingerly drew her body back down so she was lying next to him again.  “Nervous about the wedding?”<br>
<br>
