<br>
“Do you want to talk about it?”<br>
<br>
“Maybe in the morning,” she said quietly.  Bruce nodded in acceptance of her answer and wrapped his arm around her to bring her closer to him when she turned onto her other side.  <br>
<br>
“It’s okay,” he half-whispered against her bare shoulder and then placed a gentle kiss on the soft skin there.  “It’s going to be alright.”<br>
