<br>
Her brow furrowed in confusion again after the tape started.  Instead of something romantic, it appeared to be a security camera tape with an audio track that was barely clear enough to make out.  It was Lex and Bruce and they were standing outside the room that she recognized as being hers when she was in the hospital in Smallville.<br>
<br>
