The tape flickered once and new images came up on the screen.  Several clips from Gotham’s nightly news stations flashed across the set, some of them having to do with her upcoming nuptials and some having to do with the mysterious, winged vigilante that had been fighting off crime since before she moved there.  She failed to see what the connection was until the tape focused on video footage of Batman and stilled. <br>
